           move      w-ref-cod-tmo-cod    to   w-tes-tmo-orc          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A lettura e visualizzazione                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-tmo-orc-def-600.
