           move      w-tes-tmo-orc        to   w-let-arc-zoc-cod      .
           perform   let-arc-zoc-000      thru let-arc-zoc-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se codice errato : reimpostazione           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-zoc-flg    not  = spaces
                     go to slc-num-oct-900.
