      *              * pendenza                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "PV"                 to   s-ope                  .
           move      "cod-dpz"            to   s-var                  .
           move      "+"                  to   s-dop                  .
           move      "N"                  to   s-tip                  .
           move      02                   to   s-car                  .
