      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-fnd-arc-oct-toc    to   w-tes-tmo-orc          .
           move      w-fnd-arc-oct-dat    to   w-tes-dat-doc          .
           move      w-fnd-arc-oct-num    to   w-tes-num-doc          .
       fnd-arc-oct-400.
