           move      w-tes-psr-aac (1, 3) to   d-per-scr-psr-cli (3)  .
           move      w-tes-psr-aac (1, 4) to   d-per-scr-psr-cli (4)  .
           move      w-tes-psr-aac (1, 5) to   d-per-scr-psr-cli (5)  .
           move      w-tes-csr-aac (1)    to   d-per-scr-csr-cli      .
